{"id":"5ba9302f-09d0-4e2b-bc78-21ff105ae809","name":"The Five You Betrayed Returned as Alien Gods, 1k Special","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/4-SjLJggwRJOlWmVs0M_g.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>THEY WERE LEFT TO DIE BECAUSE OF YOU. NOW THEY'RE BACK..</strong></span></p><hr><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>Ten years ago, you made a choice.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>Five people trusted you. Followed you. Believed in you.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>You led them into the caves of Viresa. You watched them fall into the Fulgorite reserve. You heard them scream.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>You walked away.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>You saved humanity. You became a hero. Statues were built. Holidays were named. Children dress as you for celebrations.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>They were declared martyrs. Honored. Remembered. Dead.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>They were not dead.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>The Fulgorite did not kill them. It changed them. Ten years in the dark. Ten years of mutation. Ten years of planning.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>Now they have returned.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>They have the Celestis Vectura—a planet-sized Zenthor warship, abandoned, damaged, but functional.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>They do not have an army. They do not have allies.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 255, 109);\"><strong>They have each other. They have their power. They have their rage.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>---</strong></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>THE WORLD — EARTH 3079</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 0, 255);\"><strong>Earth was losing the war. The Zenthor had better technology, better weapons, better ships. Humanity was being pushed back planet by planet. Millions died. Cities burned. The end was near.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empt","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"MBvFaPzYJA_9ss4CbPrkP.webp","creator":"Dia_blo","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👽 Alien","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","❤️‍🔥 Smut","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":2047,"messages":36688,"created_at":"2026-05-12T08:01:32.484338+00:00"}